                            <comment id="123647" author="lexsoft" created="Sat, 8 Aug 2015 01:17:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;LustreError: 2586:0:(osd_object.c:577:osd_object_destroy()) FS-OST0000: failed to remove &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;0x100000000:0x78478:0x0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; from accounting ZAP for usr 111: rc = -2&lt;br/&gt;
